Package org.jeo.vector

Vector data model.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Feature
    An object consisting of a set of named attributes, any of which may be a vector geometry.
    VectorDataset
    A data set consisting of objects with a vector geometry, known as Feature objects.
    VectorDriver<T>
    Base interface for vector drivers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicFeature
    Basic feature implementation.
    BasicFeature.Storage  
    DiffFeature
    Feature wrapper that tracks changes to an underlying Feature object.
    FeatureCursor
    Extension of Cursor for Feature objects.
    Features
    Feature utility class.
    FeatureWrapper
    Wrapper class for Feature.
    Field
    Describes an attribute of a Feature.
    FileVectorDriver<T>
    Base class for file based vector drivers.
    GeometryTransformWrapper
    Feature wrapper that transforms a feature geometry.
    Schema
    Describes the structure of a Feature object.
    SchemaBuilder
    Builder for Schema objects.
    VectorQuery
    Describes a query against a VectorDataset dataset.
    VectorQueryPlan
    Explains how a query is handled by a format driver.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    VectorDriver.Capability
    Vector driver capability enumeration.
